         <head n="77994" xml:lang="en">
            <ref n="p.bas;1;18" type="reprint-from">P.Bas. 1 18</ref>
         </head>
         <div xml:lang="grc" type="edition" xml:space="preserve">
<ab>
    <lb n="1"/>Πᾶσις <choice><reg>Ὀρσενούφει</reg><orig>Ὀρσενούφι</orig></choice> τῶι 

    <lb n="2" rend="indent"/> ἀδελφῶι χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>τὴν γυναῖ<supplied reason="omitted">κά</supplied> μου <choice><reg>ἐκλάμβανε</reg><orig>ἐγλάνβανε</orig></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>ἄχρις ἄν <choice><reg>γένωμαι</reg><orig>γένομε</orig></choice> πρὸς σέ. 

    <lb n="5"/>Τιθο<unclear>ῆς</unclear> ἦλθεν <choice><reg>εἰς</reg><orig>ἰς</orig></choice> Θ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied><unclear>ρ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied><unclear>ν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">οῦ</supplied>

    <lb n="6" break="no" xml:id="lb6"/>θιν καὶ οἱ <choice><reg>οἰκεῖοι</reg><orig><supplied reason="omitted">οἰ</supplied>κῖοι</orig></choice> αὐτοῦ <choice><reg>εἰς</reg><orig>ἰς</orig></choice> Λητοῦς. 

    <lb n="7"/>εὐθέως <choice><reg>γινόμεθα</reg><orig>γεινόμεθα</orig></choice> ἵνα ἐκεῖ 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐργασώμεθα. καλῶς <choice><reg>ἔχω</reg><orig>ἔχωι</orig></choice> 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐνθάδε. ἐὰν ὁ θεὸς θέλῃ 

    <lb n="10"/>εὐθέως <choice><reg>ἥξω</reg><orig>ἥξωι</orig></choice> πρὸς σέ. 
</ab></div>
         <div type="commentary" subtype="linebyline">
            <list>
               <item corresp="#lb6" xml:space="preserve"><ref>6</ref> <p>BL 4.3 (κιοι → υἱοί) can be safely discarded; the reading οικιοι (or οιβιοι) is certain (P.Bas. II, p. 80 note on line 6)</p></item>
            </list>
